Wendy Morgan (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wendy_Morgan_(actress) 0 Wendy Morgan (born 1958) is an English actress. She won the award of "Best Newcomer — Actress" at the Evening Standard British Film Awards in 1980. Wendy_Morgan ( born 1958 ) is an_English_actress .
